    zh: '全灭了…'
    en: 'All gone...'
  - key: gameover.title
    zh: '虫群失联'
    en: 'COLONY LOST'
  - key: gameover.body
    zh: '最后一只洞穴虫已消失在污染与黑暗中。重建巢群，再次回应洞穴的召唤。'
    en: 'The last cave bug vanished into pollution and darkness. Rebuild the colony and answer the cave again.'
